articles.title: Pasar malam stalls block cycling path, sparks online debate
articles.content: Tables and chairs were seen blocking cycling paths at a Hougang night market. It showed a cycling path lined with makeshift night market stalls, while the pedestrian path next to it remained unobstructed.
